%F A060739 If Multinomial[a, b, c] denotes the multinomial coefficient (a+b+c)! / (a! * b! * c!) (which is an integer) then : a(n) = (-1)^(n(n-1)/2) * Product k=0, ..., n-1 Multinomial[k, k, n-1-k] = (-1)^(n(n-1)/2) * product k=0, ..., n-1 (n+k-1)!/((k!)^2 * (n-1-k)!)
